column5: I'm making my way back to the "Q" on Sunday morning. REports I've heard are the fish are on... big time! Try and get a report out early next week! Anyone else gettin out this weekend?!! HH
Nope, all done for the year  Musky closes at midnight tonight and I've been busy all day getting all my gear  cleaned up and put away for the winter........gonna be a long time till June 2nd
Going to the BOQ tomorrow. Now that muskie is closed, I have to fish for the bait fish
Im planning to hit the tribs on sunday, see if I  cant get a trout or 2
Might just hit the Credit if it doesnt rain it out... dark comes too early now anyway...
I put the boat away last week, now everyones putting them back in on GB it's wide open.
gonna take my son bait fishing ... .wanna get some pike this winter so need some chubs for bait
